message.content:
There are several suspicious processes with open sockets in the provided data:

1. Process ID 888 (firefox.exe) has a socket open on port 1168 (TCP) to 127.0.0.1.
2. Process ID 1244 (svchost.exe) has sockets open on ports 1189 and 2869 (TCP) to internal IP addresses.
3. Process ID 4 (System) has a socket open on port 139 (TCP) to the local IP address.
4. Process ID 880 (svchost.exe) has a socket open on port 1185 (TCP) to an unspecified IP address.

These open sockets could indicate network communication that may be related to the suspected phishing attack targeting alg.exe. Further analysis of the network traffic and behavior of these processes is recommended to determine the extent of the suspicious activities.
